{"name": "Bright-Hide Kobold", "type": "race", "img": "icons/creatures/reptiles/dragon-horned-blue.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>Much like their strong-claw brethren, bright-hide kobolds help make up the majority of kobold society. While the shimmer-scales have the flashier scales, the color of the bright-hide kobolds scales are bolder, brighter, and more saturated. <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Bright-hide kobolds are proud of their scales as their claim to dragon ancestry. With thicker scales, resistance to the elements, and a hardier constitution than their kin, bright-hide kobolds work as builders, tunnelers, miners, and haulers within their society.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;They tend to carry a greater disdain towards wing-beat kobolds than the rest of their brethren though, as bright-hide kobolds believe they hold the strongest tie to their ancestors, not the wing-beat kobolds.</p>", "chat": "", "unidentified": ""}, "source": "Core Rules", "portion": "core", "classDetails": "<p>Bright-Hide Kobold Traits</p><ul><li><b>Compatibility: </b>Reptile</li><li><b>Attribute Increase: </b>Your Constitution increases by 1.</li><li><b>Draconic Resilience: </b>You have resistance to the damage type associated with your draconic ancestry. The colors and their corresponding damage types are as follows:<br /><table><tr><th>Ancestry</th><th>Damage Type</th></tr><tbody><tr><td>Black</td><td>Acid</td></tr><tr><td>Blue</td><td>Lightning</td></tr><tr><td>Brass</td><td>Fire</td></tr><tr><td>Bronze</td><td>Lightning</td></tr><tr><td>Copper</td><td>Acid</td></tr><tr><td>Gold</td><td>Fire</td></tr><tr><td>Green</td><td>Poison</td></tr><tr><td>Red</td><td>Fire</td></tr><tr><td>Silver</td><td>Cold</td></tr><tr><td>White</td><td>Cold</td></tr></tbody></table></li><li><b>Tough Scales: </b>@Compendium[undertaking.abilities.6H6U8OS3L3B97ICX]{Tough Scales}</li><li><b>Elemental Spit: </b>@Compendium[undertaking.abilities.UVQHH4CUD3D9PVZR]{Elemental Spit}</li></ul>"}, "effects"